; Fighters Paradise — Trials / Tutorial index (original clean-room content, MIT).
; Lists the ordered lesson scripts the TutorialRunner walks. Each lessonN points
; at a one-[Lesson]-section .def in this directory. Lessons target the shipped
; trainingdummy command set (fireball = QCF+P). The runner auto-skips any lesson
; a loaded character cannot satisfy, so this trial loads against any character.

[Trial]
name    = "Fundamentals"
lesson1 = block.def
lesson2 = throw.def
lesson3 = fireball.def
lesson4 = antiair.def
lesson5 = combo.def
